{"tid":100155,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[粵漢不分]「 Hong Kong」就係百粵蜑家話黎！","createTime":"2017-01-29T18:02:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T19:38:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6acfba30037bf7585fab1cf330f5648ab1e7ae","tid":100155,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"游蕙禎呢D粵漢不分, 呢度成村契弟又係粵漢不分<br />\n你地知唔知「 Hong Kong」就是百粵蜑家話？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/travel/art/20120124/16009935\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftravel%2Fart%2F20120124%2F16009935&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB%2BI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=97cd1e8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftravel%2Fart%2F20120124%2F16009935&h=301d8cc1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/travel/art/20120124/16009935</a><br />\n<br />\n蜑家人是水上人，講的當然是蜑家話。蜑家話和廣東話分別不是很大，主要是水上人的生活用字特別豐富，比如「死」字，蜑家話讀做「蟬」，例句：「啲蝦再唔食就會『蟬』㗎喇！」但發音上就跟一般粵語有少少不同，沒有前圓唇元音，所以「四角裝香，洗面上床」蜑家人會講「洗角裝糠，洗面爽床」，「打魚」讀成「打椅」。相傳當年英國人於香港仔登陸，問當地人呢度叫乜名，蜑民就以蜑家話回答「糠港」，所以香港的英文名稱是「 Hong Kong」，而不是粵語拼音「 Heung Gong」。"},{"pid":"aea2e10210e93d0c27c52cc3c4ba61ff3d215180","tid":100155,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:04:49.000Z","msg":"蜑家妹真正既傳統服飾係顏色鮮艷, 兼且係收腰<br />\n你班撚人仲係度講著乜撚漢服, 都智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://premium.mingpao.com/protected/Image/20150923/_23KA011_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpremium.mingpao.com%2Fprotected%2FImage%2F20150923%2F_23KA011_.jpg&h=389f986d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3063b932bae14c97f60fdece0b8be72f542bc645","tid":100155,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:47:35.000Z","msg":"對百粵蜑族既無知, 真係好可怕！<br />\n<br />\n香港開埠後, 英治香港旗幟、匯豐銀行及皇家香港警察既警徽都有「阿群帶路圖」。該圖既故事就係百粵蜑族人阿群(陳群)引領於赤柱登岸既英商, 沿群帶路抵達港島北岸, 與粵商及漢商洽談生意既典故。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20151021/large/1445414859_66eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20151021%2Flarge%2F1445414859_66eb.jpg&h=bba48d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/49dl9y893/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2F49dl9y893%2Fimage.jpg&h=d2b4de9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百粵蜑族就係香港開埠協助英國人既原住民<br />\n<br />\n粵漢都仲未識分呀你班友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4336b6c381e12395732f4bbd85fab06443e8dba","tid":100155,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:49:17.000Z","msg":"皇家香港警察警徽中的「阿群帶路圖」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.police.gov.hk/info/img/icon/royal_logo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fimg%2Ficon%2Froyal_logo.gif&h=ae1f6bc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6052490293ef75028350ef413762f126b7867c13","tid":100155,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:07:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6cad9829263d2944e706b7f0333273621821e06","tid":100155,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T19:38:03.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲就係偷渡落嚟嘅「蝗」佔領咗<br />\n只不過過咗咁多年，到依家主權移交咗先至有返少少教養，以前嗰代全部大中華膠老而不廢老"}]}